snippet.title: Northern Song Dynasty // Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3006960/_/

A real-time strategy game based on the history of the Northern Song Dynasty. The player can experience the fun of conquering cities, directing the country, and ultimately uniting the world through their own efforts in the simulated historical background of the game!

Developed by
石家庄龙游科技有限公司
